OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,FHistory could be made at the upcoming
OL,7,FBrighton Marathon when a blind artist
OL,8,Fattempts to become the first person to
OL,9,Frun the race distance guided by remote
OL,10,Fvolunteers seeing his route through
OL,11,Fartificial intelligence (AI)
OL,12,Ftechnology.
OL,14,FThe attempt by Clarke Reynolds, 45,
OL,15,Ffrom Portsmouth, is believed to be a
OL,16,Fworld first, and will involve the use
OL,17,Fof Meta AI glasses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
