PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,FThe glasses are connected to an app -
OL,7,Fcalled Be My Eyes - which enlists
OL,8,Fvolunteers across the world to support
OL,9,Fvisually impaired people in daily
OL,10,Ftasks.
OL,12,FMr Reynolds - who is known as Braille
OL,13,Fcreative Mr Dot - is running for the
OL,14,FFight for Sight charity, and hopes his
OL,15,Fchallenge will help tackle the stigma
OL,16,Faround sight loss and perception of
OL,17,Fblind people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,FHe said: "When I got these glasses and
OL,7,Fthe app, I was thinking: what could I
OL,8,Fdo to push the boundaries of what this
OL,9,Ftechnology could do for the blind
OL,10,Fcommunity?
OL,12,F"And I thought, you know what, let's
OL,13,Frun a marathon again with complete
OL,14,Fstrangers in my ear holes."
OL,16,FMr Reynolds has the inherited
OL,17,Fcondition of Retinitis Pigmentosa and
OL,18,Fdescribes his vision like looking
OL,19,Funderwater, seeing shadows and shapes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
