PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,FHe started using the glasses last year
OL,7,Fand has also used them to go to art
OL,8,Fgalleries and have the art described
OL,9,Fto him in the voice of Dame Judi Dench.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
