PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,FConnecting the app to the glasses, the
OL,7,Fartist voice commands for Be My Eyes
OL,8,Fto be activated and gets linked up to
OL,9,Fa volunteer ready to help, who can see
OL,10,FMr Reynold's view through his glasses.
OL,12,F"By doing these things and saying I'm
OL,13,Fnot amazing, I'm not a superhero," Mr
OL,14,FReynolds added.
OL,16,F"I'm just like you, just, I found a
OL,17,Fworkaround so that I could do a
OL,18,Fmarathon, and it's just a new way of
OL,19,Fliving my life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
