PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,F"Technology is a game changer for the
OL,7,Fsight loss community. There's loads of
OL,8,Fcures to come along but we can't wait
OL,9,Ffor those cures. We've got to live the
OL,10,Fbest life we can."
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FMore than 100 people have helped Mr
OL,18,FReynolds with his training so far,
OL,19,Fincluding volunteers from the United
OL,20,FStates, Canada and a Scottish woman on
OL,21,Fholiday in Thailand.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
