OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775153468
OL,3,CBlind artist bids to become 'first to
OL,4,Crun marathon using AI glasses and app'
OL,6,FThey support him by pointing out bins
OL,7,For parked cars, as well as having
OL,8,F"amazing conversations".
OL,10,FUsually, Mr Reynolds said, the
OL,11,Fvolunteers get involved because a
OL,12,Fmember of their family have sight loss.
OL,14,FMr Reynolds previously ran the London
OL,15,FMarathon with a guide, but said "never
OL,16,Fagain" because his training relied on
OL,17,Fanother person being there throughout.
OL,19,FInstead he is finding it much easier
OL,20,Frunning with remote help, doing laps
OL,21,Fof 0.8 miles around his home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
